pick up the knife from the table

high_descs: Turn left, walk parallel to the wall on the left, and as the wall ends, turn left, walk into the corridor, enter the first room on the left, and get in front of the diningtable in the opposite corner.
Pick up the knife from the round table.
Lean upwards to reach the potato on the table.
Cut the potato on the table with the knife.
Take a small step to the left and lean downwards towards the diningtable.
Put the knife on the diningtable.
Go back to the diningtable where you can reach the sliced potato.
Pick up the potato slice from the round table.
Turn around, leave the room, go right parallel to the wall on your left, and as the wall ends, turn left and go straight to the fridge.
Put the potato slice inside the fridge, let it cool inside, then take the potato out.
Head back to the diningtable from the beginning.
Place the potato slice on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled potato slice on the oval diningtable.
